<paragraph blockId="8.[151,1436,151,835]" box="[198,875,151,178]" pageId="8" pageNumber="49">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[198,338,151,177]" pageId="8" pageNumber="49">Phenology:</emphasis>
—Flowering in February and fruiting in June.
</paragraph>
